# Client

- React 19, functional components, TypeScript
- Style with Tailwind utility classes; global styles in `src/index.css`
- API calls only through `src/lib/trpc.ts` — never raw `fetch` to the server
- Session ID lives in `src/lib/session.ts` (sent as `x-session-id` header)
- Vite proxies `/trpc` → `localhost:3001`
